STRATEGY decomposeProblem (prompt)
  Set goal to the final goal of the problem required to fulfill prompt.
  IF goal contains nothing
    Return nothing.
  SET subgoals to output of CALL decomposeGoal (goal)
	  RETURN subgoals


STRATEGY decomposeGoal (goal)
  IF goal can not be broken down into one or more tasks necessary to achieve goal
    Return nothing.
   SET subgoals to the list of tasks goal can be broken down into.
  SET goalList to an empty list
  FOREACH goal in subgoals
    Append to goalList output of CALL decomposeGoal (goal)
    RETURN goalList
